title: Congratulations to MAgIC Lab for two papers accepted by IROS 2024.
description: The papers entitled 'Dynamic Modelling of Robotic Fish with Consideration to Background Flow Using Koopman Theory' and 'Data-Driven Modeling of Ground Effect For UAV Landing on a Vertical Oscillating Platform', have been accepted and will be presented on IROS 2024 conference held in Abu Dhabi.
